{"tid":976312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一地白膠漿] 【最新預測】2030年美國霸主地位玩完","createTime":"2019-01-10T10:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:06:39.000Z","uid":111460,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"24979e7c08be2049399f3b1ff0d44da8ca32ae43","tid":976312,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:21:28.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰，特朗普積極出招，看似是美國佔盡上風，但其實，可能只是美國不能不出招，防患於未然。<br />\n<br />\n根據最新渣打集團(Standard Chartered)根據購買力平價匯率計算的名義GDP預測報告，到2030年，美國好有可能會失落全球霸主地位。<br />\n<br />\n報告預測2030年全球前10大經濟體排名如下：<br />\n<br />\n中國<br />\n<br />\n印度<br />\n<br />\n美國<br />\n<br />\n印尼<br />\n<br />\n土耳其<br />\n<br />\n巴西<br />\n<br />\n埃及<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n日本<br />\n<br />\n德國<br />\n<br />\n（榜上十大，有7個是新興國家）<br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行經濟學家David Mann解釋，排名大洗牌，主要是因為不同水平經濟體之間的人均GDP差距縮窄。報告預測，2020年時，全球會有一半人口成為中產階層；到2030年，亞洲整體佔全球GDP比例，更會由28%升至35%。<br />\n<br />\n其實如果以PPP計，關鍵在於，今次連印度都有可能超過美國，有傳媒形容為西方主導的格局將會完結。<br />\n<br />\n如果睇返近日多份報告你會發現，確有不少專家擔心美國有衰落現象；事實上已不少外資大行專家都爭相警告特朗普這一點：「美國經濟增長於未來好可能會低於2%。」<br />\n<br />\n美國政治內鬥持續，以及世行霸權動搖，再加上今次經濟體預測排名，難怪會讓人覺得，中美的優勢關係，隨時會逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E3%80%912030%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9C%B8%E4%B8%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C-040141843.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E3%2580%25912030%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259C%25B8%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%25AE%258C-040141843.html&d=51DqfOQ0AU4T8H7Q0LoiVPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6c0c5d89\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E3%80%912030%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9C%B8%E4%B8%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C-040141843.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BsNsVuW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBsNsVuW.gif&h=74caccd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2ufjWD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2ufjWD.gif&h=6026d227&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPOsa3j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPOsa3j.gif&h=5c176c89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAAY191.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAAY191.gif&h=52e91aa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b8eb4cfb349384a961603b22f169e8d985697b2","tid":976312,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"埃及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個垃圾到震既國家"},{"pid":"9a9b78ecb60d790ac07a53e4f85505aefa4cdfb1","tid":976312,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"份報告呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmethodology係點先？點計出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3d362d1210ea3e596f32a5a624d76f35d159b7","tid":976312,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b8eb4cfb349384a961603b22f169e8d985697b2","tid":976312,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"埃及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個垃圾到震既國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"土耳其，印尼又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dd0c7281dab16037e9f1917fb4aa291deb0a6e","tid":976312,"uid":35266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"佢係咪assume左<br />\n堆新興經濟體增長唔會放慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ec907